<view class="container flex-col">
  <view class="hero-panel">
    <text class="eyebrow">Midnight Season 1</text>
    <text class="title">WoWLook</text>
    <text class="subtitle">按职业、专精和属性快速定位当前赛季装备掉落</text>
  </view>

  <view class="legend-row">
    <view class="legend-pill">8 个大秘境</view>
    <view class="legend-pill">3 个团本</view>
    <view class="legend-pill">勇士 1/6 · ilvl 246</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <text class="section-title">选择职业</text>
    <text class="section-copy">职业为必选项，进入后再按专精、属性和部位筛选。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="grid-container">
    <view class="class-grid">
      <view
        wx:for="{{classes}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="class-item flex-col align-center justify-center"
        bindtap="onClassTap"
        data-key="{{item.key}}"
        data-name="{{item.name}}"
      >
        <view class="icon-wrap" style="box-shadow: 0 4rpx 20rpx {{item.color}}40; border: 2rpx solid {{item.color}}80;">
          <text class="emoji-icon">{{item.icon}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="class-name" style="color: {{item.color}};">{{item.name}}</text>
        <text class="class-armor">{{item.armorTypeName}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text>当前已接通 13 个职业数据文件结构，武僧为真实样例。</text>
  </view>
</view>
